			<description><![CDATA[<p>
<strong>The Company</strong><br />
PerkSpot (a Spotlite Brand) is a growing 25 person, 7 year old startup. We provide employee benefits solutions including our world-beating discount portal: PerkSpot.&nbsp; We provide benefits to 3 million employees at BIG employers (think: Starbucks, Walgreens, Chevron, etc.).&nbsp;&nbsp; Specifically, we build web portals where our clients&#39; employees go to find the perks and corporate discounts available to them because they work for such awesome companies.&nbsp; We help them save money, and who doesn&rsquo;t like that?&nbsp;</p>
<p>
We dress how we like, have beer on Fridays, have unlimited vacation days and we like people with lots of energy and enthusiasm.</p>
<p>
<strong>The Job</strong><br />
We are looking for an Account Representative to support the Client Account and Customer Service teams.&nbsp; You will perform a wide variety of tasks including, but not limited to:</p>
<p>
<strong>Client Support</strong><br />
Our clients enjoy having a one on one relationship with a member of our team.&nbsp; Right now we are growing faster than we can keep up.&nbsp; This is a client-facing role involving daily contact with our current clients via phone and email.&nbsp; You will be supporting our clients growing needs by providing the highest level of service and support.</p>
<p>
<strong>End User Customer Service</strong><br />
Some users need a bit of advice when navigating our offers.&nbsp; You will be our point person for helping them take advantage of our deals.&nbsp; You will need to provide quick and friendly guidance to help out, via email and phone.&nbsp;</p>
<p>
<strong>Apply If&hellip;</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
You are outgoing and enjoy interacting with all types of people throughout the day.</li>
<li>
You are organized and motivated to take on additional responsibilities as needed.</li>
<li>
Your written and verbal communication skills are top-notch.</li>
<li>
You like to work independently and prefer that we aren&rsquo;t looking over your shoulder all the time.</li>
<li>
You are excited to serve a large audience through various marketing initiatives.</li>
<li>
You are seeking an opportunity for professional growth with a small, but fast paced and growing company.</li>
<li>
You enjoy working within a team-oriented environment.</li>
</ul>
